<subSubSection pageId="485" pageNumber="486" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="485" pageNumber="486">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="485" pageNumber="486">This species extends along the Pacific Coast from central Oregon to the southern extremity of the Baja California Peninsula, and from western Arizona to southwestern Oklahoma (Kondratieff et al. 2005: 171), south to Oaxaca, Mexico [see Erwin 1970a: Fig. 109].</paragraph>
